<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>🏔️ Himalayan Store Praha</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

```
body {
  background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529654591145-d2de4e2ca3c0?w=1920&q=80');
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  background-attachment: fixed;
  font-family: Georgia, serif;
  color: #fff;
  min-height: 100vh;
}

/* Dark overlay for readability */
body::before {
  content: '';
  position: fixed;
  top: 0; left: 0;
  width: 100%; height: 100%;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
  z-index: 0;
}

.container { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 1100px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; }

/* HEADER */
header {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 50px 20px 30px;
}
header h1 { font-size: 2.8em; text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); }
header p  { font-size: 1.1em; margin-top: 8px; opacity: 0.9; }

/* NAV */
nav {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 20px;
  padding: 15px;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  border-radius: 30px;
  margin: 10px auto 30px;
  max-width: 400px;
}
nav a {
  color: #fff;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-size: 1em;
  padding: 6px 16px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  transition: background 0.3s;
}
nav a:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }

/* WELCOME */
.welcome {
  text-align: center;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 25px;
  margin-bottom: 35px;
}
.welcome h2 { font-size: 1.8em; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.welcome p  { font-size: 1em; opacity: 0.85; }

/* PRODUCTS */
.section-title {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 2em;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
  text-shadow: 1px 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
}

.products-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
  gap: 22px;
  margin-bottom: 50px;
}

.card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
  border-radius: 16px;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: transform 0.3s;
}
.card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); }

.card img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 180px;
  object-fit: cover;
}

.card-body { padding: 16px; }
.card-body h3 { font-size: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.card-body p  { font-size: 0.9em; opacity: 0.85; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.price {
  font-size: 1.2em;
  font-weight: bold;
  color: #ffd700;
}

/* ABOUT */
.about {
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 30px;
  margin-bottom: 35px;
  text-align: center;
}
.about h2 { font-size: 1.8em; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.about p  { font-size: 1em; opacity: 0.9; line-height: 1.7; }

/* CONTACT */
.contact {
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 30px;
  margin-bottom: 50px;
  text-align: center;
}
.contact h2 { font-size: 1.8em; margin-bottom: 15px; }
.contact p  { font-size: 1.05em; margin: 8px 0; opacity: 0.9; }
.contact a  { color: #ffd700; text-decoration: none; }

/* FOOTER */
footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 20px;
  opacity: 0.7;
  font-size: 0.9em;
}
```

  </style>
</head>
